## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on the topic. The perspectives included are primarily from Western educational contexts, which may not fully represent global views on standardized testing. Additionally, the report relies on secondary sources, which may introduce bias based on the authors' perspectives. Further research, including empirical studies and diverse international viewpoints, would provide a more holistic understanding of the issue.